[[Next->Story5]]

{}
You chat some more with Prof. H about your progress in the class (and make some empty promises to start future assignments much earlier) then rush out of the classroom to your next class.
[[Next->Story6]]

{"background": "hallway"}
The hallways are packed with a bustling swarm of students. Their voices ring across the hallway, sometimes interrupted with bursts of laughter. You skillfully maneuver your way through, weaving through freshmen and avoiding the seniors when suddenly-
[[Next->Story7]]

{}
!!CRASH!!
[[Next->Story8]]

{}
You fall backwards, papers flinging across the floor in scattered directions. You take a moment to collect yourself and start trying to grab your belongings, when a voice rings up from above you.
[[Next->Story9]]

{"character": "???", "portraitName": "violin", "emotion": "angry"}
Hey, watch where you're going!
[[Next->Story10]]

{}
You slowly look up to face the speaker and find yourself greeted by a fuming expression - to be more exact, a fuming expression *drenched in coffee*. He scowls at you, his foot tapping impatiently.
[[Next->Story11]]

{"relationshipChange": 5, "portraitName": "violin", "emotion": "neutral"}
His scowl lessens slightly. He seems to have accepted your apology, but continues grumbling to himself.
[[Next->Story12]]

{"relationshipChange": -5, "portraitName": "violin", "emotion": "angry"}
His scowl deepens at your response.
[[Next->Story12]]

{}
You stifle a laugh. The soloist's hair is bright pink, greatly contrasting with the nearly monotone stage. And yet, he confidently struts towards the center right next to the conductor and takes a bow.
[[Next->PreStory7]]

{"portraitName": "violin", "emotion": "angry"}
Before he can respond, you suddenly become aware of his messy curly pink hair. Wait... pink hair?
[[Um... are you the soloist from yesterday?->Story13]]

{"character": "???", "portraitName": "violin", "emotion": "blush"}
Wha-? Who-? How did you know about that?
[[Next->Story14]]

{"relationshipChange": -10, "character": "???", "portraitName": "violin", "emotion": "angry"}
