[[Oops...->Story15]]

{"relationshipChange": 5, "character": "Leo", "portraitName": "violin", "emotion": "blush"}
Woah, so you really were there!
[[Next->Story15]]

{"character": "Leo", "portraitName": "violin", "emotion": "angry"}
Well, whatever. The point is - look at the mess you've made! You better help clean this up.
[[Ok...->Story16]]

{"character": "Leo", "portraitName": "violin", "emotion": "angry"}
