[[Next->2Choice3d]]

{}
You scan the rest of the park, but you don't see anything that matches Leo's description of Deus. Disheartened, you make your way back down and shake your head.
[[Next->2Choice4a]]

{"relationshipChange": 5, "character": "Leo", "portraitName": "violin", "emotion": "sad"}
It's okay, you tried your best. Let's keep looking around!
[[Next->2Choice5a]]

